<div id="zcutoff_box">
  We recommend you to use 3.0 or bigger values for Z-score cut-offs. Z-scores &gt; 6.0 are likely to indicate evolutionary relationships and/or common folds. (See FUGUE <%= link_to "web page", "http://tardis.nibio.go.jp/fugue/prfsearch.html", :popup => true %>)
</div>
